name: Dynamism to twiddle in my sobriety

metadata.name: Fanni and the moment that never existed yet
metadata.description:
Having so many precious words yet unsaid, and many colorful moments yet unwitnessed. She is clouded with the sweetness that has never known bitterness, joy without pain, strength without pride, and above all, a glowing skin. 
She is heaven-sent, pure heart, nature lover, and has a soul that the riches of the world cannot buy.
The moment of true happiness, extraordinary emotions, magical nature, and fulfilled achievement await you as a token of your excellence. The moment where all expectations are met, and nothing more is needed.
Dedicated to my favorite.
